jpg\" /><br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t2、扉页一：学校和班级信息页<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img _load=\"1\" alt=\"3-扉页2.jpg\" id=\"aimg_3895\" src=\"http://bbs.dandang.org/data/attachment/forum/201210/13/023300x2j633dryt2xkyyy.jpg.thumb.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" title=\"3-扉页2.jpg\" /><br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t3、扉页二：借书流程示意图<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img _load=\"1\" alt=\"4-扉页3.jpg\" id=\"aimg_3896\" src=\"http://bbs.dandang.org/data/attachment/forum/201210/13/023304o71xr89ee711r5xu.jpg.thumb.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" title=\"4-扉页3.jpg\" /><br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t4、扉页三：还书流程示意图<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img _load=\"1\" alt=\"5-扉页4.jpg\" id=\"aimg_3897\" src=\"http://bbs.dandang.org/data/attachment/forum/201210/13/0233089eskge1k0jfl2gjk.jpg.thumb.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" title=\"5-扉页4.jpg\" /><br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t5、扉页四：图书角管理员信息A<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img _load=\"1\" alt=\"6-扉页5.jpg\" id=\"aimg_3898\" src=\"http://bbs.dandang.org/data/attachment/forum/201210/13/023313dd3snim3d363d73d.jpg.thumb.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" title=\"6-扉页5.jpg\" /><br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t6、扉页五：图书角管理员信息B<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img _load=\"1\" alt=\"7-扉页6.jpg\" id=\"aimg_3899\" src=\"http://bbs.dandang.org/data/attachment/forum/201210/13/023319fygcfrrgh1v7g69y.jpg.thumb.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" title=\"7-扉页6.jpg\" /><br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t7、扉页六：致小朋友的一封信<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img _load=\"1\" alt=\"8-登记页.jpg\" id=\"aimg_3900\" src=\"http://bbs.dandang.org/data/attachment/forum/201210/13/023324ku222ex2bdxujold.jpg.thumb.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" title=\"8-登记页.jpg\" /><br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t8、图书借阅登记表<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img _load=\"1\" alt=\"9-封底.jpg\" id=\"aimg_3901\" src=\"http://bbs.dandang.org/data/attachment/forum/201